# Discord Bot Elemental - AI Assistant Rules

## Project structure

- Root files: `package.json`, `railway.json`, `Procfile`, `.nvmrc`, `README.md`, `.cursorrules`, `CHANGELOG.md`, `bot.js`
- Data files: `data/*.json`
- Documentation: `docs/`

## Development approach

- Keep bot logic in `bot.js` until a planned modular split.
- Make game-specific behavior configurable rather than hardcoded when possible.
- Never copy old game knowledge text into this repo.

## Critical release rules

1. Always update `CHANGELOG.md` before every push to `main`.
2. Newest version entry must be first (`## [x.y.z]`) in semver order.
3. Verify deployment posts to both release/debug channels after push.
4. Never commit secrets (`.env`, tokens, webhook URLs).
